ract","text":"From Proto-Semitic *yad-, whence was derived the root ي د ي (y d y)."},"ipa":["/jad/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n44787","headword_ar":"يَدٌ","root":"yd","body":[{"kind":"text","text":"The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"arm, from the shoulder-joint to the extremities of the fingers."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Msb.) ―         -b2-  [The"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"foreleg"},{"kind":"text","text":"of a horse, &c.] ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yadN bayoDaA='u","text_ar":"يَدٌ بَيْضَا=ءُ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aboyaDu","text_ar":"اَبْيَضُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places, near the end of the paragraph. ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yadN","text_ar":"يَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"A"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"sleeve:"},{"kind":"text","text":"see R. Q. 1 in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*b","text_ar":"ذب"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yadu Alqawosi","text_ar":"يَدُ القَوْسِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"rijolN","text_ar":"رِجْلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places. ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"TiwaAlu AlA^ayodi","text_ar":"طِوَالُ الاَيْدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlA^ayodiY","text_ar":"الاَيْدِى"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"vamaAniyapN","text_ar":"ثَمَانِيَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aEoTaAhu","text_ar":"اَعْطَاهُ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Eano yadK","text_ar":"عَنْ يَدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", as occurring in the Kur, ix., 29,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He gave it in acknowledgement of the superiority of the receiver;"},{"kind":"text","text":"that the power ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yado","text_ar":"يَدْ"},{"kind":"text","text":") of the latter was superior to that of the giver: or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"because of favour received;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from subjection and abasement:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(M:) or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from compulsion:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(A 'Obeyd, T:) or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"obediently:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"walking with it; not riding, nor sending it:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in ready money."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asolama EalaY yadaYo fulaAnK","text_ar":"اَسْلَمَ عَلَى يَدَىْ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He became a Muslim by the advice and persuasion of such a one."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Marg. note in a copy of the Jámi' es-Sagheer, on a trad. commencing"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mano","text_ar":"مَنْ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^asolama","text_ar":"اَسْلَمَ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^axa*t~u Einodahu yadFA","text_ar":"اَخَذتُّ عِنْدَهُ يَدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ax*","text_ar":"اخذ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b10-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lifulaAnK EinodiY yadN","text_ar":"لِفُلَانٍ عِنْدِى يَدٌ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I owe such a one a benefit."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b11-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY yadihi","text_ar":"عَلَى يَدِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"By his agency,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"means."},{"kind":"text","text":"See the corresponding expression in Hebrew, in Ps. lxiii. 11, Jer. xviii. 21, and Ezek. xxxv. 5, in the phrase “ to pour out (the blood of) a person by means of the sword. ” ―         -b12-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walaA tuloquwA biA^ayodiykumo A_ilaY Alt~aholukapi","text_ar":"وَلَا تُلْقُوا بِاَيْدِيكُمْ اـِلَى التَّهْلُكَةِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Kur, ii. 191): see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"b","text_ar":"ب"},{"kind":"text","text":"(used redundantly). ―         -b13-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lA","text_ar":"لا"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A=tiyhi yada Ald~ahori","text_ar":"ا=تِيهِ يَدَ الدَّهْرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yada Almusonadi","text_ar":"يَدَ المُسْنَدِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I will not come to him,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"do it, ever; I will never do it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, in I., voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"musonadN","text_ar":"مُسْنَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".) See"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^abadN","text_ar":"اَبَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jadFA","text_ar":"جَدًا"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b14-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY yadaYi","text_ar":"عَلَى يَدَىِ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alxayori waAlyumoni","text_ar":"الخَيْرِ وَاليُمْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xayorN","text_ar":"خَيْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b15-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biEotuhu yadFA biyadK","text_ar":"بِعْتُهُ يَدًا بِيَدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"naAjizN","text_ar":"نَاجِزٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b16-  You say, also,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"baAyaEotuhu yadFA biyadK","text_ar":"بَايَعْتُهُ يَدًا بِيَدٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":", the two nouns being only thus used, as a denotative of state,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I contracted a sale with him for ready money; i. q."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"biAlt~aEojiyli waAln~aqodi","text_ar":"بِالتَّعْجِيلِ وَالنَّقْدِ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Mgh.) ―         -b17-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laka A^ano yakuwna ka*aA","text_ar":"لَكَ اَنْ يَكُونَ كَذَا"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yadaY~a","text_ar":"يَدَىَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"?]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yadiY~a","text_ar":"يَدِىَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is like"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY~a","text_ar":"عَلَىَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"lk An ykwn k*A","text_ar":"لك ان يكون كذا"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Aboo-Sahl El-Harawee, TA in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Hbq","text_ar":"حبق"},{"kind":"text","text":".) ―         -b18-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^utiYa EalaY yadi fulaAnK","text_ar":"اُتِىَ عَلَى يَدِ فُلَانٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ataY","text_ar":"اَتَى"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b19-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^aw~ala *iY yadayoni","text_ar":"اَوَّلَ ذِى يَدَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*aAti yadayoni","text_ar":"ذَاتِ يَدَيْنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"*w","text_ar":"ذو"},{"kind":"text","text":". ―         -b20-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"taHota yadihi","text_ar":"تَحْتَ يَدِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Under his authority."},{"kind":"text","text":"―         -b21-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yadN","text_ar":"يَدٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Generosity."},{"kind":"text","text":"(A, voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aborN","text_ar":"شَبْرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"source_refs":["M"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}